# New service checklist

Before marking a service complete:

- [ ] `README.md` with purpose, run instructions, and env vars
- [ ] `Dockerfile` (and compose service stub when local-dev ready)
- [ ] `/healthz` (and `/readyz` if dependent on Kafka/DB/etc.)
- [ ] Structured JSON logging
- [ ] Automated tests wired into `make test` for that language
- [ ] Module registered in `go.work` if Go, or package manifests if Python/TS
- [ ] Relevant keys added to root `.env.example` with phase TODO comments

Do not merge skeleton services that only compile without health, logging, and tests.
